long_description: The Green Trails McDowell Mountains map offers a beautifully detailed topographic guide to the Arizona's McDowell Sonoran Preserve and McDowell Mountain Regional Park. Printed on waterproof and tear-resistant paper, this map stands up to the rigors of your outdoor adventure. Map features a scale of 1:35,000. The Green Trails McDowell Mountains map measures 24 x 18 in. (9 x 6 in. folded). Green Trails Maps; copyright 2012.
